# MediumShip landing (apps/www) web client env
# Copy to `apps/www/.env.local` for local dev.
#
# The landing only needs the public Convex URL — the product demo reads the
# guest-first public feed (no Clerk auth required).

NEXT_PUBLIC_CONVEX_URL=

# Optional: if omitted, the scripts fall back to `../../.env.local`.
